pageContext.claim: “Now you know that's a totally unsubstantiated charge, really? It's not unsubstantiated, it's fact. Joe's son, Hunter, got thrown out of the navy and then he became a genius on Wall Street two days.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump bumbles the chronology of Hunter Biden’s life. Biden joined a Delaware bank where he was quickly promoted after law school, but did not join the Navy Reserves until later. He was discharged from the Reserves after he failed a drug test.
